Description: 15 fragments of papyrus extracted from cartonnage with demotic text, in most cases just on one side.
Curator's comments: The fragments come from at least three different texts (on the basis of the appearance of the papyri). There are traces of writing usually only on one side of each fragments and the larger pieces also have clear margins. Very little text is legible, but one small piece (left-hand centre) has the end of three lines of figures.
